---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import Turbine from '../../Images/ewp-strut-connections-hero.jpg'
import HomeTurbine from '../../Images/home-50kw-turbine.jpg'
import MobileTurbine from '../../Images/home-mobile-turbine.png'
import Arrow from '../../Images/arrow.svg'
---

<section class="container">
    <Image class="content-image" src={Turbine} alt='Up close view of the turbine'/>
    <div class="content content-background">
        <h1>Eastern Wind Power</h1>
        <section class="text">
            <h2>Who is EWP?</h2>
            <p>Eastern Wind Power, Inc. (EWP), based in Cambridge, Massachusetts, has designed, built and tested a Sky Farm™ 50 kW Vertical Axis Wind Turbine (VAWT) to be roof mounted on high-rise buildings, or pole mounted in open, high wind areas. We have joint ventured with Siemens Industry, Inc. which has developed our generator and inverter system. We have designed a mobile unit particularly for disaster relief applications. We also provide a 30 kW system with the same turbine design.</p>
            <p>As of September 2011, our full-scale prototype Sky Farm™ 50 kW is NSTAR grid connected, producing power, and has undergone durability testing at the Martha’s Vineyard Airport in Edgartown, Massachusetts. EWP is conducting blade icing tests  with 3M and DuPont coatings on our blade fixed on top of Mt. Washington, NH – through the courtesy of the Mt. Washington State Park.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="turbine-tech">
            <h2>Our Turbine Technology</h2>
            <div class="turbines-container">
                <div class="turbine">
                    <Image class="Turbine-image" src={HomeTurbine} alt="Image of 50K Turbine" />
                    <h3>50kw Turbine</h3>
                    <a href="/50KwTurbine" >View Details
                        <Image class='blue-arrow' src={Arrow} alt='Blue Arrow Icon'/>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="turbine">
                    <Image class="Turbine-image" src={MobileTurbine} alt="Image of Mobile Turbine" />
                    <h3>Mobile Turbine</h3>
                    <a href="/MobileTurbine" >View Details
                        <Image class='blue-arrow' src={Arrow} alt='Blue Arrow Icon'/>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .content-image {
        padding-top: 20px;
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        position: relative;
        z-index: -1;
    }

    .content {
        margin-bottom: 90px;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 35px 15px 50px;
        
        section {
            margin-bottom: 90px;
        }

        section:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: black;
        }

        .text {
            text-align: left;

            p {
                color: #1B1A22;
            }
        }
    }

    .turbines-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 75px;

        .Turbine-image {
            max-width: 350px;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .turbine {
            text-align: left;

            img {
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

            h3 {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            a {
                color:#1E4459;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;

            }

            @media (width >= 768px) {
                a {
                    justify-content: start;
                }
            }

            .blue-arrow {
                margin-bottom: 0;
                margin-left: 12px;
            }
        }
    }

    @media (width >= 768px) {

        h1 {
            font-size: 42px;
        }

        .content {
            margin-top: -125px;
            padding: 35px 50px 50px;
        }

        .turbines-container {
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 100px;
        }
    }
</style>